<section xml:id="sec-volume-by-shells">
  <title>Volume by shells</title>

  <objectives>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <p>
          Compute volume by adding the contributions of thin cylindrical shells.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Use shell height and radius to quantify each shell's contribution.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Choose shells or washers based on which method aligns with the region's geometry.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </objectives>
  
  <introduction>
